page.title: 03TYPES OF HOMES
page.content: In our area we have 7 main types of homes.Terraced,semi_detached,detached, maisonettes,local flint houses,flats and bungalows.Most of our area is filled with terraced and semi detached. {Terraced_ }We saw a lot of terraced houses.They were made of bricks and tiles.The gardens are small and some have sheds.The sheds are made out of gravel. {Semi detached_ }The semi detached houses are made of bricks and tiles the gardens are a bit bigger than the terraced.They have sheds as well sa the terraced they are made of gravel. {Detached_ }some of the detached houses were made of bricks and tiles some where stone some where flint.They had big gardens.
